{"tid":628492,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔計要對客的工，有冇人間公司工作期間完全冇人敢玩電話?","createTime":"2018-04-14T02:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T12:02:50.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18f283c0eb84bb8430f6a1c873639fc59e24cdaa","tid":628492,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:14:26.000Z","msg":"我公司入面，就算唔駛對客的同事都好，冇人敢喺office hour玩電話，寧願搵啲嘢扮工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我就差唔多一半時間玩電話，但公司又出唔到warning letter又炒唔到我先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似有啲公司冇人敢準時走，偏偏我係最準時走嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 長週用緊電話開post中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5611ce5abcd93533f3af1213654fa10f5d90ee3b","tid":628492,"uid":82082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"點解出唔到warning/炒你？"},{"pid":"009985fe3871c1dbccaaa5b7f083808bee681104","tid":628492,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"成日玩電話對眼好攰<br />\n我平時都係訓教多"},{"pid":"c3d02275df0c8ebd71ea10e4c65e9e24c96a9d94","tid":628492,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5611ce5abcd93533f3af1213654fa10f5d90ee3b","tid":628492,"uid":82082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"點解出唔到warning/炒你？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"青山走犯"},{"pid":"92a70d3066e964f3432d270b13810bb107b011f7","tid":628492,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3d02275df0c8ebd71ea10e4c65e9e24c96a9d94","tid":628492,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5611ce5abcd93533f3af1213654fa10f5d90ee3b","tid":628492,"uid":82082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"點解出唔到warning/炒你？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14